import React from 'react'
import Fade from 'react-reveal/Fade';
import {Container ,Title,Desc,Row,Col,Content} from './style'
const Popular = () => {
    return (
        <Container>
            <Title>Most Popular Tools</Title>
            <Desc>Tools for the best Designers and Developers
            most popularly used in the world</Desc>

            <Content>
               <Row>
               <Fade bottom>
                        <Col>
                              salom1
                        </Col>
                </Fade>
                  
                <Fade bottom>
                       <Col>
                              salom2
                       </Col>
                 </Fade>

                  <Fade bottom>
                       <Col>
                              salom2
                       </Col>
                 </Fade>
               </Row>

               <Row>
               <Fade left>
                        <Col>
                              salom1
                        </Col>
                </Fade>
                  
                <Fade bottom>
                       <Col>
                              salom2
                       </Col>
                 </Fade>

                  <Fade right>
                       <Col>
                              salom2
                       </Col>
                 </Fade>
               </Row>
            </Content>
        </Container>
    )
}

export default Popular
